Package: CASSIA
Title: Collaborative agent system for single-cell interpretable annotation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Elliot Yixuan", "Xie", email = "xie227@wisc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: CASSIA (Collaborative agent system for single-cell interpretable annotation) provides R wrappers for a Python-based single-cell annotator.
    It uses reticulate to interface with the Python backend for cell type analysis and batch processing.
